Production Security Best Practices

•
Rate Limit Requests: Restrict OTP requests per IP and phone number (e.g., maximum 3 requests per 15 minutes) to prevent SMS pumping attacks.

•
Never Expose API Keys: Keep ENVOISMS_API_KEY strictly on the backend server.

•
Session Bound: Associate the returned session_id with the authenticated user's temporary state or JWT token rather than trusting raw client payload parameters.

